{"tid":948384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東大嶼人工島　中原地產主席施永青：填海好　何必講利益","createTime":"2018-12-20T04:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T05:18:05.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e6d79032f731de6dfce0d11f99108760ca0c0030","tid":948384,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:31:52.000Z","msg":"我們在考慮填海這類公共工程時，根本不應該純以能否收回金錢上的成本作為主要考慮。因為由政府負責進行的很多公共工程，都是以服務市民為目的的。有時是完全不收費的；難道政府應該以收不回成本而拒絕興建？<br />\n<br />\n例如：政府為防止山泥傾瀉，保護市民安全而興建的護土牆，就不會向途經的人收費。當然如果政府財政能力不足的話， 亦只能降低對安全性的要求，暫時放棄在一些受影響的人較少的地方建護土牆。台灣在興建橫貫公路初期，就沒有財力在所有有塌方危險的路段都建護土牆。<br />\n<br />\n填海是為了造地去解決香港的市區發展需要，內裏既有市民的住屋需要，亦有經濟發展需要。我們在考慮要不要填海時，應考慮的是香港是否真有這種需要，與香港是否真有這種承擔能力。如果增加市區發展用地是香港的基本需要，而香港又不是負擔不起的話，我們根本不應該因可能沒法收回建設成本而拒絕填海。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/新聞/填海為民-何必曰利-149698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E5%A1%AB%E6%B5%B7%E7%82%BA%E6%B0%91-%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%85%E6%9B%B0%E5%88%A9-149698&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=869f72bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/新聞/填海為民-何必曰利-149698</a><br />\n<br />\n施永青話唔好講利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c878297d0b9ac580fff7c5c9d88ea0b6f35311da","tid":948384,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:33:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb324b46d0565f55d5d7dcd9b134cd7452f95471","tid":948384,"uid":8048,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:34:55.000Z","msg":"感謝施生提供笑話"},{"pid":"7efea9c4cbfda28a5f6d6d660eac0b8c6101647a","tid":948384,"uid":1380,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:36:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"807d1a45fd552ca4f7d69f1ec87eca24c43babb1","tid":948384,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"填海造陸過聖誕"},{"pid":"e2f6214c363b0d70791021e8ef2379ca89d810db","tid":948384,"uid":60297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:45:48.000Z","msg":"同警察係政治中立一樣咁難聽"},{"pid":"1e0d54d067725c1c65a64acf9035cca9bca60e5a","tid":948384,"uid":177590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"聖誕節仲講咁多<br />\n寄聖誕卡啦"},{"pid":"03976a19b02cb9a49fed7e94ee07f19987900025","tid":948384,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:46:49.000Z","msg":"你免費幫年青人上樓囉"},{"pid":"2c980a7f07042ecab1a3c88e3bad88d2ef6b816c","tid":948384,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"由地產霸權嘅婊婊者講出依句說話<br />\n真係特別有說服力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4259756bc6a04b984105e88f938e2b2a267aad5","tid":948384,"uid":155137,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:56:56.000Z","msg":"施生搞生意都係求打和 良心地產商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9039ba0a4330505c58bbe1de317f86600a9e0a7a","tid":948384,"uid":8785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:58:00.000Z","msg":"搞手為求打個和"},{"pid":"d23d6e2c590a206db35915440fcdd47a9f05a695","tid":948384,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:59:44.000Z","msg":"攞護土牆同你可以起樓賺暴利嘅工程比<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地產商每賣一個單位，政府收50%稅，我咪讚成填海囉"},{"pid":"cbf1bf1c22c54eafe225612be22d4503feb624d5","tid":948384,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:18:05.000Z","msg":"地產佬實係咁講，不意外"}]}